        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "## Stability Constants of Uranium(VI) with Crown Ethers — NIST SRD-46\n\n### Result: **No data found**\n\nDespite an exhaustive search across all crown ether ligands catalogued in SRD-46:\n\n| Ligand ID | Crown Ether | vlm_count (all metals) |\n|---|---|---|\n| ligand_9672 | 12-Crown-4 | 3 |\n| ligand_9674 | 15-Crown-5 | 45 |\n| ligand_9675 | Benzo-15-crown-5 | 3 |\n| ligand_9676 | 18-Crown-6 | 76 |\n| ligand_9677 | A-Dicyclohexyl-18-Crown-6 | 42 |\n| ligand_9678 | B-Dicyclohexyl-18-Crown-6 | 39 |\n| ligand_9679 | Benzo-18-crown-6 | 2 |\n| ligand_9680 | Dibenzo-18-crown-6 | — |\n| ligand_9681 | 3-Hydroxymethylbenzo-18-crown-6 | — |\n\n**The NIST SRD-46 database contains no stability constant entries for uranium(VI) / uranyl (UO₂²⁺) with any crown ether ligand.** The metal entity \"uranyl\" (UO₂²⁺) does not appear to be registered in the SRD-46 metals catalog at all.",
